data.description: This Duplex is located on a Quiet Street in West Oak Lane. It is conveniently located within walking distance to schools, shopping and public transportation. Each unit has 2 Beds and 1 Bath. Second floor is occupied. First floor is available. Each Unit need some repairs  and updating .  Both units have the following amenities: On and Off Street Parking & Garage (with opener); Secured  private front  door entry for each unit;  The 1st floor unit,  has access to the basement for additional living space. 2st floor has a open floor plan, large bedrooms and ceiling fans. This duplex is being sold in "As is Condition." Whether you are an investor, or plan to live there, duplexes like this one do not come along often. Don't delay, make your appointment today.
